abstract: >
  Silvina is an AI-powered editorial assistant designed to automate manuscript validation
  for Spanish-language academic journals. The system integrates document structure analysis,
  Spanish APA 7 reference validation, EUMIC guideline compliance, and local large language
  model (LLM) support for grammar and style review, enabling accurate, privacy-preserving
  editorial workflows.

